<HEADLINE>
EL CAMINO HIGH SCHOOL REPEATS ACADEMIC DECATHLON VICTORY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY JASON KANDEL  
 c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News  
 
<TEXT>
