<HEADLINE>
POISON PEN LETTERS: HAPPY VALENTINE'S DAY, YOU FATHOUSE PIG 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
